title: 367.40 DEFINITIONS.
text:
For purposes of this chapter, the following terms shall have the meanings given them.
"Peace officer" has the meaning assigned in section 626.84.
MS 2004 [Repealed, 2005 c 10 art 2 s 5]
MS 2004 [Repealed, 2005 c 10 art 2 s 5]
"Part-time peace officer" has the meaning assigned to it in section 626.84.
